The paper deals with face verification using deep learning techniques and image synthesis. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also uses a pre-trained Convolutional Neural Network (CNN) and proposes a synthesis network based on generative adversarial networks (GANs), which are popular in the sub-categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also deals with image processing and manipulation, which falls under the sub-category of cs.MM (Multimedia). Finally, the paper deals with face recognition and verification, which is a topic of interest in the sub-category of cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
